src/parallel/ll-dgr-src/poststream_g.f File Reference

Detailed Description

Post-Stream step for the pressure distribution function g in the parallel dual grid D2Q9 Lee-Lin multiphase LBM.

All differential terms are calculated using a second order centered differencing scheme.
